 \displaystyle \int_t^{t+1} \left(\sum _{k=0}^{\infty } \sin \left(\frac{\pi  k}{2}\right) \frac{B_k(z)}{u^k}\right) \, dz=\sum _{k=0}^{\infty } \sin \left(\frac{\pi  k}{2}\right) \frac{t^k}{u^k}=\frac{t u}{t^2+u^2}\\ \displaystyle \int _t^{t+1}\frac{u}{2} (\psi ^{(1)}(z+i u)+\psi ^{(1)}(z-i u))dz=\frac{t u}{t^2+u^2} 
 \displaystyle \sum _{k=0}^{\infty } \sin \left(\frac{\pi  k}{2}\right) \frac{B_k}{u^k}=\frac{u}{2} (\psi ^{(1)}(i u)+\psi ^{(1)}(-i u))\\ \displaystyle -\frac{1}{2 u}+\sum _{k=2}^{\infty } \sin \left(\frac{\pi  k}{2}\right) \frac{B_k}{u^k}=-\frac{1}{2 u}-\frac{2 \pi ^2 u}{\left(e^{\pi  u}-e^{-\pi  u}\right)^2} 
